	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64590169"><p>This is the conundrum of many green projects.   They aren't cheap, but they are cheaper than *not* doing them.</p><p>The savings are long term and significant but harder to measure in 'less damage clean up' from climate change, while the price is up front and clear.</p></div>
